mark_description_description: The mark consists of the letter "A" in stylized, uppercase font, wherein the letter is formed by an incomplete triangle at the top and a curved concave line that forms the horizontal line in the letter. The curved concave line intersects the left vertical line of the triangle but does not intersect with the right vertical line of the triangle and therefore forms a space between the curved concave line and the right vertical line of the triangle.
